Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveTina Lawson, Mother of award-winning singer, Beyonce, and Solange Knowles, is celebrating her marriage of seven years with her husband Richard Lawson.
Tina, on her Instagram page, shared a photo of herself and her husband.
She captioned it, “@mrrichardlawson, I Could not let the day pass without letting you know what a gift from God you have been in my life. My love, my main Road Dawg , my always listening ear and biggest motivator! These 7 years have flown by !! To many more!!! on our 7th Anniversary Happy Anniversary.”
The couple got married in 2015.
